title: The new iPhone emojis are here
text:
The new iPhone emojis are here! 
CNN Money Thursday 22nd October, 2015 
ADSPACE-END --> The hotly anticipated (by emoji nerds) iOS 9.1 includes more than 150 new emoji characters. There's a burrito, a middle finger, new happy faces and a robot. There are religious buildings, a realistic squirrel and turkey, and a giant hunk of cheese. Another new addition in iOS 9.1 is just for iPhone 6S users....
